div.div:
Calibration is performed by in execute() overridden method summing samplesToAverage new measurements and after that calculating the offset (sensors that don't need to calibrate just do nothing).
Calibration method returns time that this calibration will take (in seconds). After this time you can get new calibration values using getOffset() method.
